  "title": "SENIOR ARCHITECT / SENIOR ARCHITECTURAL ASSOCIATE",
  "description": "<p>1) Candidate who have experience in mixed used Commercial / Residential and Public Development with minimum 8 years’ experiences. Candidate who have experience in Healthcare Development and Institutional experience is preferred.<br /></p><p>2) BOA Registered Architect is preferred.<br /></p><p>3) Good knowledge and well versed in Singapore Building Regulations and Codes, Design Development and Detailing.<br /></p><p>4) Must be capable of being a Team Leader and take responsibility in managing projects independently without supervision.<br /></p><p>5) Excellent interpersonal and communication skill.<br /></p><p>6) Good working attitude, proactive and conscientious.<br /></p><p>7) Self-motivated with good time management skill.<br /></p><p>8) Ability to supervise and manage a team in achieving project goals, targets and milestone dates.In addition.</p>",
